task.en: Save the current empty table to Documents, naming it with "GDP PPP Data".
task.zh: 将当前空白表格保存到Documents目录下，文件名就叫"GDP PPP Data"。
task.ar: قم بحفظ الجدول الفارغ الحالي في مجلد Documents، وقم بتسميته "GDP PPP Data".
task.ja: 現在の空の表をDocumentsフォルダに「GDP PPP Data」という名前で保存してください。
task.ru: Сохраните текущую пустую таблицу в папке Documents, назвав её "GDP PPP Data".

pre_command.en: osascript -e 'tell application "Pages" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Keynote" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to activate' && sleep 5 && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to tell (make new document with properties {document template:template "Blank"}) to tell table 1 of sheet 1 to set {column count, row count, header row count, header column count} to {2, 4, 0, 0}'
pre_command.zh: osascript -e 'tell application "Pages" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Keynote" to quit without saving' && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to activate' && sleep 5 && osascript -e 'tell application "Numbers" to tell (make new document with properties {document template:template "空白"}) to tell table 1 of sheet 1 to set {column count, row count, header row count, header column count} to {2, 4, 0, 0}'
